Class VidStreamReq

java.lang.Object
us.mn.state.dot.tms.client.camera.VidStreamReq
public class VidStreamReq extends Object
VidStreamReq: Video-stream-request parameters. Data class that contains the parameters needed to open a video stream. The VidPanel class uses the static VidStreamReq.getVidStreamReqs(...) generator method to convert a Camera reference to a list of VidStreamReq objects that "should" be able to stream video from that camera to the current client.
Author:
John L. Stanley - SRF Consulting
